title: People who feed birds impact conservation

title_detail.value: People who feed birds impact conservation

summary: Researchers analyzed how people who feed birds notice and respond to natural events at their feeders by collaborating with Project FeederWatch, a program that engages more than 25,000 people to observe and collect data on their backyard birds.
